---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Dubai Golden Visa Through Property Investment 2026 — Complete Guide | Horizon Dubai Property" description="Get a 10-year Dubai Golden Visa by investing AED 2M+ in property. Step-by-step guide: requirements, eligible properties, application process, family inclusion, benefits.">

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-navy">Home</a> /
      <span class="text-gray-700">Golden Visa Guide</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 font-serif">Dubai Golden Visa Through Property Investment: Complete 2026 Guide</h1>

    <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-gold p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-10">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Key Takeaway</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">The UAE Golden Visa grants a 10-year renewable residency to property investors who purchase real estate worth AED 2,000,000 (~$545,000 USD) or more. It covers the investor, spouse, and children. No minimum stay requirement — you can maintain your visa while living abroad.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: March 2026 | Reading time: 12 min</div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">What Is the UAE Golden Visa?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">The UAE Golden Visa is a long-term residency visa that allows foreign nationals to live, work, and study in the UAE without a national sponsor. Introduced in 2019 and expanded significantly in 2022, it has become one of the world's most attractive residency-by-investment programs.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-10">For property investors, it means: buy a property worth AED 2M+ and receive a 10-year renewable residency visa for yourself and your family.</p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">Property Investment Requirements</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-10">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <thead><tr class="bg-gray-50"><th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold border-b">Requirement</th><th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold border-b">Details</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y">
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Minimum Investment</td><td class="p-4">AED 2,000,000 (~$545,000 USD)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Property Type</td><td class="p-4">Residential (apartment, villa, townhouse). Off-plan accepted if developer is approved.</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Ownership</td><td class="p-4">Must be freehold. Property can be fully paid or mortgaged (equity must be AED 2M+).</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Multiple Properties</td><td class="p-4">You can combine multiple properties to reach the AED 2M threshold.</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Visa Duration</td><td class="p-4">10 years, renewable indefinitely as long as property is retained.</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Family</td><td class="p-4">Spouse + children included. Parents can be added separately.</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Minimum Stay</td><td class="p-4">No minimum stay requirement (unlike previous 5-year visa).</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4 font-medium">Work Permit</td><td class="p-4">Golden Visa includes the right to work in the UAE.</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">Step-by-Step Application Process</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-gold font-bold">1</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Purchase Qualifying Property</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Buy property worth AED 2M+ in a freehold zone. Complete DLD registration and obtain title deed (Oqood for off-plan).</p></div></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-gold font-bold">2</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Obtain Title Deed</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Get your property title deed from Dubai Land Department. This is the primary document for visa application.</p></div></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-gold font-bold">3</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Apply via ICP or GDRFA</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Submit Golden Visa application through the Federal Authority for Identity and Citizenship (ICP) or General Directorate of Residency and Foreigners Affairs (GDRFA).</p></div></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-gold font-bold">4</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Medical & Emirates ID</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Complete medical fitness test and biometrics for Emirates ID. Process takes 2-4 weeks.</p></div></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"><span class="text-gold font-bold">5</span></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Receive Golden Visa</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Golden Visa stamped in passport. Emirates ID card issued. Family applications can be processed simultaneously.</p></div></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">Golden Visa Benefits</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-5"><p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">10-Year Residency</p><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Renewable indefinitely. No sponsor required.</p></div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-5"><p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Family Inclusion</p><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Spouse and children automatically included.</p></div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-5"><p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">No Minimum Stay</p><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Unlike other visas, no requirement to be in UAE 180 days/year.</p></div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-5"><p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Work Permission</p><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Right to work in the UAE or start a business.</p></div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-5"><p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Banking Access</p><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Open UAE bank accounts, access financial services.</p></div>
      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-5"><p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Education & Healthcare</p><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Access to UAE schools and healthcare system.</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-serif">Costs Breakdown</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-10">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <thead><tr class="bg-gray-50"><th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold border-b">Item</th><th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold border-b">Cost</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y">
          <tr><td class="p-4">DLD Registration Fee</td><td class="p-4">4% of property value</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4">Agency Commission</td><td class="p-4">2% of property value</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4">Golden Visa Application</td><td class="p-4">~AED 4,000-6,000 ($1,100-1,600)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4">Medical Test</td><td class="p-4">~AED 500 ($135)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4">Emirates ID</td><td class="p-4">~AED 370 ($100)</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="p-4">Health Insurance (required)</td><td class="p-4">AED 3,000-10,000/yr ($800-2,700)</td></tr>
          <tr class="font-semibold"><td class="p-4">Total Transaction Cost</td><td class="p-4">~7-8% of property value + visa fees</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 font-serif">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I get a Golden Visa with off-plan property?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, off-plan properties from RERA-approved developers qualify. The property must be valued at AED 2M+ and the developer must be registered with the Dubai Land Department.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I combine multiple properties for the AED 2M threshold?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Yes, you can combine multiple properties to reach the AED 2,000,000 minimum. All properties must be in your name and registered with DLD.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What if I have a mortgage on the property?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">You can qualify if your equity in the property is AED 2M+. For example, if you buy a AED 3M property with AED 2M down payment and AED 1M mortgage, you qualify.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How long does the Golden Visa process take?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Typically 2-4 weeks from application to visa stamping. Some fast-track services can complete it in 1-2 weeks.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I sell the property after getting the Golden Visa?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">If you sell the qualifying property, the Golden Visa may be revoked unless you purchase another qualifying property. It's advisable to maintain property ownership for visa validity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-navy to-royal rounded-2xl p-8 text-center text-white">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 font-serif">Get Your Golden Visa</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Marina will help you find Golden Visa eligible properties, handle the purchase, and manage your visa application end-to-end.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/properties/" class="bg-gold text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gold-dark transition-colors">Golden Visa Properties</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/971528486680" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">WhatsApp Marina</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I get a Golden Visa with off-plan property?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes, off-plan properties from RERA-approved developers qualify if valued at AED 2M+." }},
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I combine multiple properties for the AED 2M threshold?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes, you can combine multiple properties registered with DLD to reach AED 2,000,000." }},
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How long does the Golden Visa process take?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Typically 2-4 weeks from application to visa stamping." }},
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I sell the property after getting the Golden Visa?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The visa may be revoked unless you purchase another qualifying property." }}
    ]
  })} />

</BaseLayout>
